column2: SELECT dbo.fIAUFromEq(s.ra, s.dec), s.specobjId, s.ra, s.dec, p.z, p.zErr, s.class, j.g, s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid FROM Photoz p JOIN specobj s ON s.bestObjId = p.objId JOIN PhotoObj j ON j.ObjId = p.objId  WHERE  (s.ra BETWEEN # AND # OR s.ra BETWEEN # AND #)  AND s.z <= #  AND photoErrorClass=#  AND p.zErr <= #  AND s.dec BETWEEN # and #  AND (class = &&&)  AND s.zWarning = #  ORDER BY p.z DESC
